  "bodyHtml": "<main class=\"product-page product-page-ai\"> <section class=\"section split-section\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">AI 光學分選</p> <h1>面向高價值塑膠回收的光學分選設備</h1> <p class=\"hero-copy\">蔚澜 AI 光學廢棄物分揀器可依材質與顏色辨識 PET 瓶、HDPE 瓶、PP 及其他混合塑膠。模組化配置支援自動廢棄物分選系統、MRF 設備升級及緊湊智慧回收設施，適用於需要穩定連續分選的場景。</p> <div class=\"hero-actions\"> <a class=\"text-link is-hud\" href=\"/contact\">請求提案</a></div></div> <picture> <source srcset=\"/assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.webp\" type=\"image/webp\"> <img src=\"/assets/images/recyclable-plastic-sorting-line.png\" alt=\"AI 可回收塑膠光學分選線\"></picture></section> <section class=\"section\" id=\"models\" aria-labelledby=\"models-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">型號資料</p> <h2 id=\"models-title\">型號範圍由模組化光學分選配置定義</h2> <p>三種配置共用 AI 分選平台，可依吞吐量與物料類別選擇。</p></div> <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-ai\"> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-1\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-01</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V1-5</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">迷你</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:35%\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.6&ndash;0.8<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:55%\"> <dt>動力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">30<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:38%\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">24<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·8 × 3 m 版面 ·3 m 淨空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:50%\"> <dt>分選範圍</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">5<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明 PET·有色 PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合塑膠\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · color PET · HDPE · PP · mixed plastics\">PET ·HDPE ·PP ·混合</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-2\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-02</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V2-9</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">標準</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:58%\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">0.8&ndash;1.2<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:78%\"> <dt>動力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">45<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:62%\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">36<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·12 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:90%\"> <dt>分選範圍</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">9<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明 PET·綠 PET ·藍色 PET ·混色 PET·白 HDPE·有色 HDPE·PP ·混合塑膠·剔除\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·混合·剔除</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-ai is-tier-3\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">SYS-03</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">GL01V3-10</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">Plus</p></div> <span class=\"spec-card-status\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <i></i><i></i></span></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:95%\"> <dt>處理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">1.5&ndash;2<small>t/h</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\"> <dt>動力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">53<small>千瓦</small></span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:92%\"> <dt>佔地面積</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">51<small>m<sup>2</sup></small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">安裝面積 ·17 × 3 m 版面 ·6 m 淨空高度</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <dt>分選範圍</dt> <dd class=\"spec-scope\"><span class=\"spec-value\">10<small>物料類型</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix spec-scope-summary\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-label=\"完整分選範圍：透明 PET·綠 PET ·藍色 PET ·混色 PET·白 HDPE·有色 HDPE·PP ·PE ·混合塑膠·剔除\" data-scope-detail=\"clear PET · green PET · blue PET · mixed-color PET · white HDPE · colored HDPE · PP · PE · mixed plastics · reject\">PET 顏色 ·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·剔除</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article></div></section> <section class=\"section sorting-performance-section\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-performance-title\"> <div class=\"sorting-performance-head\"> <div> <p class=\"eyebrow\">性能資料</p> <h2 id=\"sorting-performance-title\">分選性能由識別、控制與可改造模組共同驅動</h2> <p>GL01V 系列結合 AI 識別、光學感測、氣流噴射、循環輸送及數位報告，打造一個緊湊的塑膠回收與 MRF 升級分選中心。</p></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-feed-panel\" aria-labelledby=\"sorting-feed-title\"> <div> <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">穩定給料材料</p> <h3 id=\"sorting-feed-title\">物料識別範圍</h3></div> <div class=\"sorting-feed-grid\" aria-label=\"常見塑膠流範例\"> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-clear\"><b>PET</b><small>透明</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-green\"><b>PET</b><small>綠色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-blue\"><b>PET</b><small>藍色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pet-mixed\"><b>PET</b><small>混色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe\"><b>HDPE</b><small>白色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-hdpe-colored\"><b>HDPE</b><small>有色</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pp\"><b>PP</b><small>剛性</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-pe\"><b>PE</b><small>目標</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-mixed\"><b>混合</b><small>塑膠</small></span> <span class=\"sorting-feed-chip chip-reject\"><b>剔除</b><small>流</small></span></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-data-band\" aria-label=\"GL01V 性能資料指標\"> <div class=\"sorting-data-copy\"> <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">緊湊型分選中心</p> <h3>回收率與佔地面積資料</h3> <p>Mini、Standard 和 Plus 的配置從緊湊的試點產線擴展到更大型的 MRF 分選升級，同時保持相同的 AI/HUD 操作邏輯。</p> <div class=\"sorting-mode-switch\" aria-label=\"版面狀態\"> <span>工作</span> <span>運輸</span></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-data-grid\"> <article> <span>分類</span> <strong>10<small>類上限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>處理能力</span> <strong>2<small>t/h 上限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>動力</span> <strong>30<small>千瓦下限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>佔地面積</span> <strong>24<small>m<sup>2</sup> 下限</small></strong></article> <article> <span>佈局</span> <strong>滑架<small>安裝</small></strong></article> <article> <span>快速改裝</span> <strong>17<small>天最快</small></strong></article></div></div> <div class=\"sorting-smart-panel\"> <div class=\"sorting-feature-intro\"> <p class=\"sorting-panel-kicker\">智慧機器</p> <h3>操作員控制介面</h3></div> <div class=\"sorting-feature-grid\" aria-label=\"分選中心優勢\"> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-ai\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>AI 識別</h3> <p>更高的回收價值：AI 可辨識 PET、HDPE、PP、PE 與混合塑膠，降低對人工判斷的依賴。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-air\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>氣噴分選</h3> <p>穩定輸出純度：快速的氣流噴射能精確移除目標，同時處理線保持連續通量。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-sensors\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>感測器控制</h3> <p>降低純度風險：即時感測器訊號能在輸出品質下降前，暴露識別、壓力、時序及物料流漂移。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-rate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>96-98% 分選率</h3> <p>96-98% 分揀性能：手冊中列出的準確度支援高純度回收目標，用於塑膠回收與 MRF 升級。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-robot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>可接入機器人的佈局</h3> <p>降低勞動壓力：可接入機器人的佈局留有空間減少手工挑選，隨著物料量增加。</p></article> <article> <span class=\"sorting-feature-icon icon-cockpit\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <h3>數位座艙</h3> <p>更快的決策：即時狀態、警報、運行時間、分選統計、碳排放指標和視訊串流都整合在同一個畫面中。</p></article></div></div></section> <section class=\"section dark-section product-process-section\" aria-labelledby=\"plastic-process-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">工藝流程</p> <h2 id=\"plastic-process-title\">工藝控制從穩定給料延伸到數位化報告</h2> <p>光學分選系統圍繞明確的物料路徑組織，讓專案團隊可據此評估給料、預分選、物料分選、顏色分選及營運資料在產線中的作用。</p></div> <ol class=\"process-timeline\" aria-label=\"塑膠回收流程\"> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-01</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>穩定給料</h3> <p>以受控速率將消費後瓶子或混合的可回收塑膠放入分選線。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"穩定給料過程影片\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI上料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 你的瀏覽器不支援影片播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-02</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>預分選介面</h3> <p>在下游分揀前，先將金屬貨櫃與其他材質製成的瓶子分開。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"預分類流程影片\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI预分.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 你的瀏覽器不支援影片播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-03</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>物料識別分選</h3> <p>依目標樹脂類別分隔塑膠，以提升回收價值並減少人工依賴。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"物料分揀過程影片\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI分拣.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 你的瀏覽器不支援影片播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-04</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>顏色識別分選</h3> <p>依照顏色 PET 瓶及其他目標材料分組，專案價值取決於較乾淨的比例。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"色彩分類過程影片\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\"> <video controls playsinline preload=\"metadata\"> <source src=\"/assets/video/AI出料.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\"> 你的瀏覽器不支援影片播放。</video></div></figure></div></li> <li class=\"process-timeline-step\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-rank\">SYS-05</span> <div class=\"process-timeline-card\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-body\"> <h3>數位化報告輸出</h3> <p>追蹤吞吐量、類別、設備狀態、警示及碳相關操作指標。</p></div> <figure class=\"process-timeline-media\" aria-label=\"數位化報告輸出影片佔位符\"> <div class=\"process-timeline-video\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"影片即將推出\"> <span class=\"process-timeline-video-tag\">CAM-05</span> <span class=\"process-timeline-video-play\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span> <span class=\"process-timeline-video-label\">影片即將推出</span></div></figure></div></li></ol></section> <section class=\"section product-compare-section\" aria-labelledby=\"compare-title\" hidden> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">對比資料</p> <h2 id=\"compare-title\">對比資料覆蓋佔地面積、產能、功耗與組裝效率</h2> <p>以下對比圍繞佔地、產能、功耗與組裝效率，協助評估光學分選線的總擁有成本。</p></div> <div class=\"product-compare-layout\"> <figure class=\"product-compare-explode\" aria-label=\"GL01V爆炸視角\"> <div class=\"product-compare-explode-frame\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"爆炸視圖即將推出\"> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-tag\">爆炸 ·GL01V2-9</span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:18%;--pin-y:32%\" data-label=\"01\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:38%;--pin-y:58%\" data-label=\"02\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:58%;--pin-y:26%\" data-label=\"03\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:74%;--pin-y:64%\" data-label=\"04\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-pin\" style=\"--pin-x:88%;--pin-y:40%\" data-label=\"05\"></span> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-label\">爆炸視角即將登場</span></div> <figcaption> <span class=\"product-compare-explode-meta\">5 模組化滑橇·標準模具</span></figcaption></figure> <div class=\"product-compare-panel\"> <header class=\"product-compare-panel-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-self\"></span>蔚澜 GL01V</span> <span class=\"product-compare-legend\"> <span class=\"product-compare-legend-mark is-base\"></span>產業基準</span></header> <ul class=\"product-compare-list\" role=\"list\"> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-01</span> <h3>局部與整機比例</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">單位成本的百分比</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:38%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">38%</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">62%</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">較低的備件比率意味著折舊較慢，且壽命週期維護成本更低。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-02</span> <h3>佔地面積</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">標準層的 m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:55%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">36 m²</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">65 m²</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">滑架安裝布局適合緊湊的 MRF 房間及路邊回收站。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-03</span> <h3>處理能力</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">t/h，標準等級</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:88%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.8 – 1.2</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:62%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">0.6 – 0.9</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">優化給料 + AI 識別能提升相同佔地等級的吞吐量。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-04</span> <h3>功耗</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">kW，標準等級</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:60%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">45 kW</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:100%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">75 kW</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">按額定吞吐量計算，每噸分揀功率約降低40%。</p></li> <li class=\"product-compare-row\" data-better=\"true\"> <div class=\"product-compare-row-head\"> <span class=\"product-compare-row-id\">M-05</span> <h3>運輸與組裝</h3> <span class=\"product-compare-row-unit\">現場安裝天數</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bars\"> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-self\" style=\"--fill:35%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">3 – 5 天</span></div> <div class=\"product-compare-bar is-base\" style=\"--fill:90%\"> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-label\">基線</span> <span class=\"product-compare-bar-value\">10 – 14 天</span></div></div> <p class=\"product-compare-row-note\">預接線滑架模組以標準貨櫃出貨；現場工作主要為螺栓固定與線纜連接。</p></li></ul></div></div></section> <section class=\"section ai-faq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-faq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">常見問題</p> <h2 id=\"ai-faq-title\">配置判斷從物料資料、產出目標與現場介面開始</h2> <p>這些答案有助於回收業者、EPC 團隊及設備採購者評估蔚澜 AI 光學分選機是否適合其物料流及專案階段。</p></div> <div class=\"ai-faq-panel\"> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-01</span>物料分離範圍</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">該系統設計用於可回收塑膠流，如 PET 瓶、HDPE 瓶、PP、混合硬塑膠，以及顏色基 PET 組分，包括透明、綠色、藍色及混合色瓶。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>物料照片或影片</span> <span>目標產出類別</span></div></article> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-02</span>價格因素依據</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">價格取決於吞吐量、物料類別、分選模組數量、穩定給料與打包範圍、數位控制需求、安裝支援，以及專案是否需要與現有 MRF 設備整合。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>目標吞吐量</span> <span>分選模組範圍</span></div></article> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-03</span>光學分選產能範圍</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">GL01V 系列覆蓋 0.6-2 t/h。最終選型應結合物料組成、污染程度、目標純度、可用佔地面積及每日運行時間進行評估。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>每日營業時間</span> <span>可用佔地面積</span></div></article> <article class=\"ai-faq-item\"> <h3 class=\"ai-faq-question\"><span>Q-04</span>現有設施整合</h3> <p class=\"ai-faq-answer\">當專案方提供當前流程佈局、進料狀況、輸送帶高度、控制需求及目標產出時，即可評估整合性。滑架結構支援實務改裝討論。</p> <div class=\"faq-input-list\"> <span class=\"faq-input-label\">所需輸入</span> <span>既有產線佈局</span> <span>輸送帶高度與控制點</span></div></article></div></section> <section class=\"section ai-rfq-section\" aria-labelledby=\"ai-rfq-title\"> <div class=\"section-heading\"> <p class=\"eyebrow\">RFQ 輸入資料</p> <h2 id=\"ai-rfq-title\">尺寸選型精度取決於物料資料、吞吐量、產出與佈局輸入</h2> <p>在報價前將這些輸入資料送出，讓工程團隊能確認分選範圍、設備型號、佈局可行性及整合風險。</p></div> <div class=\"ai-rfq-checklist\"> <article> <span>01</span> <h3>物料照片或影片</h3> <p>顯示輸送帶的進料流、打包狀況、污染程度及正常運作條件下的顏色混合。</p></article> <article> <span>02</span> <h3>目標吞吐量</h3> <p>確認每小時處理能力、每日營運時間、尖峰負載，以及該處理線是否需要一個或多個分選模組。</p></article> <article> <span>03</span> <h3>產出類別</h3> <p>列出所需的產出組分，例如透明 PET、綠色 PET、藍色 PET、HDPE、PP、混合塑膠或剔除流。</p></article> <article> <span>04</span> <h3>既有產線佈局</h3> <p>提供輸送帶高度、可用佔地面積範圍、上游供料方式、下游打包機位置及控制介面需求。</p></article></div> <div class=\"rfq-action-strip\"> <a class=\"primary-button\" href=\"/contact\">請求工程評審流程</a> <a class=\"secondary-button\" href=\"/resources\">準備檔案包</a></div></section></main>"
}
